# -*-perl-*-

=head1 NAME

REDUCE_SCAN_QL - Recipe for processing SCAN data

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This recipe processes SCAN data from the quick-look pipeline.

=head1 AUTHOR

Andy Gibb E<lt>agg@astro.ubc.caE<gt>

